Step 1: Install Yarn
npm install --global yarn

Step 2: Create New Nuxt 3 Project with npx
npx nuxi@latest init <your-project-name>

Step 3: Install Dependencies
yarn install

Step 4: Install Pinia
npx nuxi@latest module add pinia

Step 5: Install I18n translations
npx nuxi@latest module add i18n

Step 6: Run Application
yarn dev

Step 7: Build and Start Production
yarn build
yarn start